							항목입니다.</b>
					</div>
					<div class="mt-3 col-12">
						<table class="table table-bordered">
							<tbody>
								<tr>

									<td width="20%" class="bg-light">아이디 <b
										class="text-danger">*</b></td>
									<td width="80%" class="pb-0 pt-0">
										<div class="row mb-0 pb-0 pt-2">

